# 🇷🇴 ShuddhiCheck AI – Phase II: Romania Readiness

This folder contains the official readiness brief and rollout strategy for ShuddhiCheck AI’s Phase II expansion into Romania.

📄 [Download Romania Readiness Brief (PDF)](./ShuddhiCheckAI_PhaseII_Romania_Readiness.pdf)

---

## 📌 Key Highlights

- GDPR oversight by ANSPDCP (Romanian DPA)
- National digital health development under eHealth Romania
- Pro-U.S. alignment and EU AI Act adoption trajectory
- High need for compliance modernization in rural and oncology settings

---

## 🏛️ Governance & Innovation Partners

- Ministry of Health – Romania
- ANSPDCP (Romanian Data Protection Authority)
- Ministry of Research, Innovation and Digitalization
- Romanian eHealth Association
- Regional pilot clusters: Bucharest, Cluj-Napoca, Iași, rural EU-funded regions

---

## 🌐 Language & Localization

| Language   | Status |
|------------|--------|
| **Romanian** | ✅ Official; required for public rollout and regulatory communication |
| **English**   | ✅ Used in health IT, startup, and research spaces |

🟢 Bilingual platform recommended for pilots (Romanian + English)

---

## 🛠️ Next Steps

- Upload the PDF readiness brief
- Begin outreach to ANSPDCP and Ministry of Health
- Launch pilot-ready dashboard in Romanian for selected hospitals
